snippet.title: The Snyderverse IS Happening and Here Is Why...
snippet.description:
In the past 10 days, 4 things have happened that have led fans to think that Snyderverse is truly happening. Zack Snyder has teased something like this before, and it led to the Snyder Cut being released, so it looks like it could be happening again!
